Omumu   ọnwa nke mbụ, na abalị asatọ na afọ 1949 (odi afọ iri asaa na atọ) na Benin City no na Naijiria.Ag
umakwukwo   College des Frères Chrétiennes.
Ronald Chagoury (a mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị nke asatọ n'ọnwa Jenụwarị n'afọ 1949) bụ onye ọchụnta ego Naijiria, onye nchoputa (ya na nwanne ya nwoke Gilbert Chagoury), na onye isi oche nke Chagoury Group.
A mụrụ Ronald Chagoury na Naịjirịa na abalị asatọ na onwa nke mbu, na afọ 1949, nwa Ramez na Alice Chagoury, bụ ndị si Lebanon kwaga n'afọ 1940
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na College des Frères Chrétiens na Lebanon, ma gụọ ọmụmụ azụmahịa na Mahadum California State, Long Beach, US.
Chagoury lụrụ Berthe, ha nwere ụmụ abụọ.
Aha Chagoury apụtawo na Panama Papers.
